author: The Critical Drinker
description:
Well, its finally here. Time to find out if Snow White was movie magic, or if everyone was rooting for the poisoned apple. And with Assassin's Creed Shadows releasing today, we'll talk about the controversies and PR disasters that have blighted one of the most troubled games ever made. Join me, MauLer, Despot of Antrim, Verbal Riot and Lady Gravemaster for Open Bar 135. 

Subscribe to Despot: https://www.youtube.com/@DespotofAntrim
Subscribe to Verbal Riot: https://www.youtube.com/@verbalriotshow
Subscribe to Lady Gravemaster: https://www.youtube.com/@LadyGravemaster
title: Open Bar #135 - Snow White Verdict, Assassins Creed Shadows, Hollywood's Box Office Collapse
